      "index": 1,
      "text": "Email Sequence\nA drip campaign is usually based on your user's behavior.\nLet's say you want to create the following campaign:\n- Send every user a welcome email when they join.\n- If a user received an email: wait a day and then follow-up with pro user tips meant for highly engaged users.\n- Otherwise: wait for up to three days and then send them the default trial offer, but only if the user hasn't already upgraded their plan in the meantime.\nThis page provides an overview on how to use Inngest to build reliable marketing campaigns, as well as all the related materials to this feature.",
      "char_count": 589,
      "token_count": 124,
      "metadata": {
        "title": "#### On this page",
